  "method": [
    "Heat the oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat. Add the seitan, broccoli, and bell pepper and cook over medium heat for 3 minutes. Add the cucumber, carrot, and artichoke hearts. Stir and cook for 1 minute. Take off the heat.",
